+
+## Lithe controls
+
+lithe-privacy-header = Lithe privacy
+
+lithe-ai-protection-toggle =
+  .label = AI & tracker protection
+  .accesskey = A
+
+lithe-ai-protection-description = Blocks known trackers, fingerprinters, cryptominers, and Firefox AI surfaces; strips common tracking parameters and sends Global Privacy Control. It cannot control how a site uses information you deliberately submit.
+
+lithe-vibes-toggle =
+  .label = Vibes local discovery
+  .accesskey = V
+
+lithe-vibes-description = Opens a dedicated discovery tab. Vibes sends DuckDuckGo only generic category searches, pre-reads at most three candidates without cookies, and classifies them with a bundled MIT-licensed model. Its interest profile stays in this profile and never reads general browsing history.
